Design a modern Web3 fintech mobile app called "BGR Pay".

Style:
- Clean, minimal, professional fintech
- Dark mode first
- Color palette: deep black background (#0B0F1A), primary blue (#2563EB), white text, green accent for cashback
- Typography: Inter or SF Pro, large titles, clear hierarchy

Screens to design (iPhone 14 – 390x844):
1. Onboarding screen with logo "BGR Pay", tagline "Pay. Earn. Control.", and a primary button "Connect Wallet"
2. Home screen showing BGR balance card, two main actions ("Pay", "Swap"), and a cashback summary card
3. Payment screen with amount input, token selector (BGR), and a primary button "Pay now"
4. Success screen with confirmation icon and text "Payment successful" and "+3% BGR cashback"
5. Finance screen with simple expense chart and monthly summary
6. Transaction history screen with list of payments, swaps, and cashback entries

Include:
- Rounded cards
- Soft shadows
- Modern icons (wallet, payment, chart)
- Clear CTA buttons
- Consistent spacing and alignment

Deliver a production-ready UI suitable for investors and early users.
